{"tid":2214881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰繼續於小紅書分享化妝心得　眼部素顏超沒神采嚇窒網民","createTime":"2020-09-23T14:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T14:38:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7258b3a480e8a36b60e42056f3c1abe8a38ecb","tid":2214881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"現年39歲的范冰冰自從2018年經歷逃稅風波與陰陽合同之後，演藝事業嚴重受挫，至今仍未能復出拍戲，不過她就月前已重新活躍於社交網，亦有在網上直播平台力sell自家護膚品牌的產品，親自做生招牌帶貨推銷，吸金力驚人。<br />\n<br />\n冰冰還經常在小紅書上素顏示範如何化妝護膚，分享心得，完全無懼以真面目示人。早前她就於小紅書上分別post了自己有畫眉化眼妝以及沒有畫眉化上眼妝的照片，兩個樣子予人截然不同不同的感覺。她留言表示：「我眼中的自己和愛我的他們眼中的我」形成了強烈的對比。而冰冰沒有化眼妝的容貌，在她的唇妝映襯之下，雙眼顯得更加沒神采，兼且有點驚嚇。"},{"pid":"858009207146fa4201ab25ef6f2e1949eed72df4","tid":2214881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200923/385443630069977088.jpeg/CAUC8nESfrC9gx7hGGewQnlplk02XVZ2gZ3Vs4Gd1bM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200923%2F385443630069977088.jpeg%2FCAUC8nESfrC9gx7hGGewQnlplk02XVZ2gZ3Vs4Gd1bM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=118692e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200923/385445213180661760.png/03XUTrAPA9bT9X4Gv9BEcUiPv-X9XzeWeURLNXlESzU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200923%2F385445213180661760.png%2F03XUTrAPA9bT9X4Gv9BEcUiPv-X9XzeWeURLNXlESzU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d1e1a640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200923/385445216510939136.png/I8327FHlApswS6s8dM0-i4YT2eAiVZIoPSKVij0ilYo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200923%2F385445216510939136.png%2FI8327FHlApswS6s8dM0-i4YT2eAiVZIoPSKVij0ilYo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e9fc0e88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1343ddbb2c65118609078a7b76865ef917ddfe49","tid":2214881,"uid"